WEBVTT

00:00:00.560 --> 00:00:04.312
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for joining me again today.

00:00:04.313 --> 00:00:09.970
We really appreciate y'all always showing up and praying with us. It's such a blessing.

00:00:09.971 --> 00:00:23.038
We really prayed hard last night and I believe we've seen a lot of results, all to the glory of God. Isn't that amazing? It's kind of like putting a fire out.

00:00:23.039 --> 00:00:29.735
It's like you have a fire extinguisher and you can see it kind of going across the world—a defusing of things right now.

00:00:29.736 --> 00:00:43.344
You can see all the things that are happening in the world right now with all the major articles that Braden found today, with even President Trump and Israel saying don't strike Iran right now and the other Arab nations.

00:00:43.345 --> 00:00:55.919
And I thought, well, isn't that interesting? It felt like it was a volcano that was getting ready to explode yesterday as I was interceding all day long.

00:00:55.920 --> 00:01:01.565
We could feel the pressure of this thing mounting and mounting.

00:01:01.566 --> 00:01:16.580
It was to the point where I told Diana, 'This thing is about to go off right now.'It felt so imminent, but the Lord said, 'This can't be done by yourself.

00:01:16.581 --> 00:01:30.010
You're going to have to have corporate intercession.'So He said, 'Bring it to the people and pray last night over what we were seeing.'And so that's what we did.

00:01:30.011 --> 00:01:41.139
I want to show you some of the articles that came in the news today that Braden found that I believe are a result of all of us praying.

00:01:41.140 --> 00:01:56.394
You had the WWPs praying with Sister Billy and her group, and there's a lot of you that come from over there to our broadcast, and we're so grateful for every single one of you.

00:01:56.395 --> 00:02:04.656
I want to show... do you have any of those articles? Yes. Germany. This is what I thought was kind of interesting.

00:02:04.657 --> 00:02:11.833
Remember I told you when I was looking in the spirit, I felt, 'Don't—you're going to escalate this if he goes after NATO...

00:02:11.834 --> 00:02:27.625
if he goes after Greenland.'I felt such a red light, green light, and the Lord was showing us this is going to burn bridges so greatly with Europe if he does this.

00:02:27.626 --> 00:02:34.701
Now, a lot of people say, 'I don't care if he burns bridges or not.'Go back to that article.

00:02:34.702 --> 00:02:50.719
'Germany and other NATO allies sending troops to Greenland amid Trump threats.'So they're sending troops to defend Greenland against the United States of America.

00:02:50.720 --> 00:03:05.036
And I thought, that says something—that our allies are sending their troops to defend a nation against us because I said it will come across as a bully.

00:03:05.037 --> 00:03:16.760
I said this will affect the midterms; I saw this affecting midterms and it was very negative.

00:03:16.761 --> 00:03:22.310
There's a lot of people who said, 'Brandon, I just don't believe that we'll lose any kind of seats in the House or the Senate.

00:03:22.311 --> 00:03:26.872
We're going to do a landslide home run again just like we did in 2024.

00:03:26.873 --> 00:03:38.798
We're going to do it in 2026 and we're just going to do all this.'I said this is where the Lord said, 'Don't underestimate your enemy.

00:03:38.799 --> 00:04:00.459
Don't underestimate the darkness on both sides.'I'm not going to sit here and say everything is always bright and sunny on the Republican side, but I'm going to tell you, for the most part, a lot of the way that the Republicans vote is biblical Christian values, and so that's why we always sway that way.

00:04:00.460 --> 00:04:12.158
But the Lord said, 'Don't underestimate your enemy. You must pray for President Trump to finish his term.

00:04:12.159 --> 00:04:26.705
You must pray for him to finish, live long, finish strong, and not just barely getting by, but flourish.'There was a major door last night that we were seeing when we got up to it.

00:04:26.706 --> 00:04:37.359
I saw this major door that was a beautiful door. It was glowing with all this beautiful light, but it was a door for only Trump to go through.

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:42.319
It involved major decisions that he was going to make to get through this door.

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:58.354
But in front of this door was a black fence that had briars and rose bush thorns wrapped into it, and we had to cut it back.

00:04:58.355 --> 00:05:06.982
I know it's symbolic, okay? It's not a real door. For all you baby Christians that are just coming on here, this is not a real door; this is a spiritual door.

00:05:06.983 --> 00:05:09.768
There's something in the spirit realm the Lord's trying to show us.

00:05:09.769 --> 00:05:22.079
So we are opening that door by faith, praying over whatever this door is that the Father has for President Trump.

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:37.198
As for the briars, we prune them back. We're taking everything off, opening and making the gate possible to get through in the spirit realm. All this is bathed in prayer; this is symbolic.

00:05:37.199 --> 00:05:47.982
So the Lord showed us that door and we were to undergird him in prayer by lifting his hands and praying over these doors that the Lord has for him.

00:05:47.983 --> 00:06:01.877
For He said, 'This is a door that I have presented for him, but you've got to obey this in prayer for a major assignment.'So we saw that door and we saw that assignment last night.

00:06:01.877 --> 00:06:12.638
I could see us hacking away with a machete in the spirit realm or a sword, cutting back those thorns and those briars so that he could walk through and do what he's supposed to do.

00:06:12.639 --> 00:06:17.251
That's what the body of Christ is called to do—to pray for our leadership.

00:06:17.252 --> 00:06:25.462
Pray for our governors, our mayors, our police department, whoever is protecting this.

00:06:25.463 --> 00:06:36.269
We pray for our leadership. And so that's what we did last night. We saw that, and then I saw again the red light, green light.

00:06:36.270 --> 00:06:46.849
The Lord was showing me about the troops, praying for the troops, praying for the secret intel—our friends.

00:06:46.850 --> 00:06:59.155
The Lord will not allow me to say a lot of what I saw last night for the safety of our people who are trying to protect our nation.

00:06:59.156 --> 00:07:08.246
I'm just going to bypass it and move on because I don't want to get a spanking, and for their safety, it's just better.

00:07:08.247 --> 00:07:17.519
But okay, this is what we're going to do. We're going to go over some of these other articles. Do you have any more articles?

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:30.154
'Israel and Arab nations ask Trump to refrain from attacking Iran for right now.'I thought that was interesting. That's what I'm saying.

00:07:30.155 --> 00:07:42.745
That's a—I believe that is a defusing and trying to, because of what they're getting on the ground, us praying for the people that are in harm's way.

00:07:42.746 --> 00:07:52.634
And this article could be old news right now—I don't know when he got this—but it just came out today.

00:07:52.635 --> 00:08:32.639
So, very interesting. Any other news? Then you had Russia. Russia says blackmail and threats against Cuba are unacceptable.

00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:48.750
We already know that I saw Russia reaching out to Cuba, trying to have an underground alliance like the 1960s Cuban missile crisis.

00:08:48.751 --> 00:09:11.359
The Lord said, 'Watch old alliances, for they'll try to be rebirthed.'And I saw Russia giving biological weapons to Cuba and they put them underneath the ground in Cuba.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:19.970
I saw 50-gallon drums. I saw a vial—it looked like a cylinder sphere thing with a biohazard on it.

00:09:19.971 --> 00:09:35.033
And the Lord showed me this was a planned future attack through mules against America through Florida—down in Florida, Miami in particular.

00:09:35.034 --> 00:09:43.771
And so the Lord showed us all that. Well, we see Russia coming to bat for Cuba because they needed Cuba, but they wanted Venezuela.

00:09:43.772 --> 00:09:49.168
They wanted Colombia. They want all the alliance for the BRICS.

00:09:49.169 --> 00:10:00.398
But this is what I was seeing when we were diffusing and taking apart their foundation of what they wanted.

00:10:00.399 --> 00:10:08.697
Little by little, they get in a panic. It's putting the bear in a corner. And I saw us poking the bear.

00:10:08.697 --> 00:10:32.601
Remember how many times I said, 'Be careful poking the bear.'As I saw President Trump cracking his whip, and in the visions in the past, he was standing on that stand and he was cracking his whip and he was making the bear pause and the dragon pause, and for this season, they were pausing.

00:10:32.602 --> 00:10:45.518
But the Lord said, 'Watch how they pause just for a season.'It doesn't mean that they stop forever. They just pause. A lion tamer can only get the lion to pause.

00:10:45.519 --> 00:10:59.119
And He said, 'I will use him right now to get some stuff done so that the body of Christ can move around and get things done more freely than what they could have if Kamala Harris would have been on the scene.

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:19.039
I will use him to get the church ready for a major outpouring of My spirit for what you're about to see, for the greatest move of God we've ever seen before.'And I saw the Lord using him again for finances as he was pedaling at the canoe trying to keep the economy from going over the side.

00:11:19.040 --> 00:11:24.012
They said, 'Brandon, you say a lot of stuff about the economy.

00:11:24.013 --> 00:11:31.439
You say, "How come we haven't seen anything?"'Then this is Satan's wheelhouse. This is what he's best at is finances.

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:40.705
And this is not going to take somebody being limp-wristed, sitting there being idly getting by going, 'Well, God, you're just going to rain it down on me.'You have to...

00:11:40.706 --> 00:11:51.679
The Lord said, 'If you want this next wealth transfer, you're going to have to contend for it.'Be a contender.

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:59.679
How bad do you want it? How bad are you willing to pray and come against because we are in the end of the end?

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:03.370
How bad do you want the wealth transfer? How bad do you want it, church?

00:12:03.371 --> 00:12:07.952
You're not just going to sit idly by and pluck it like ripe cherries off a tree.

00:12:07.953 --> 00:12:15.053
The Lord showed me that you're going to have to be listening to Him every single step of the way.

00:12:15.054 --> 00:12:21.796
Listening to the Father's voice so that you don't hear the stranger's voice on when to invest, what to invest in, and when to get out.

00:12:21.797 --> 00:12:25.683
Know when to hold them, know when to fold them, know when to walk away, know when to run.

00:12:25.684 --> 00:12:33.092
Like Kenny Rogers, you've got to count your money when you're sitting at the table. It's serious.

00:12:33.093 --> 00:12:40.220
But most people think, 'Well, it's just going to happen,'and you just, 'Oh, I feel sorry for myself.'Nobody feels sorry for you.

00:12:40.221 --> 00:12:43.124
That's what the Lord told me. He said, 'Nobody feels sorry for you.

00:12:43.125 --> 00:12:48.479
Nobody feels sorry for My cry. Nobody feels sorry for the wealth transfer. How bad do you want it?

00:12:48.480 --> 00:12:57.857
How bad do you want to be hearing Me for what I'm going to tell you to do to get the wealth from the wicked laid up for the righteous?'You're going to have to take the land; be a contender.

00:12:57.858 --> 00:13:04.428
David had to go and slay the giant. David had to go and take the land from the Philistines.

00:13:04.429 --> 00:13:10.905
He didn't sit back idly by and say, 'Well, God, will you just help do it all for me?'No.

00:13:10.906 --> 00:13:34.178
The Lord said, 'Put your boat into motion and I will anoint you to get it done.'And most people in the body of Christ have a passive mentality of 'God, will you just help me do it?'because they've been taught some kind of fable or a mailbox mentality and think that it's just going to happen.

00:13:34.179 --> 00:13:39.119
The Bible says that He'll bless whatever you put your hands to.

00:13:39.120 --> 00:13:44.317
And most people don't want to go out and contend for it. What is He telling you to do?

00:13:44.317 --> 00:13:54.231
Whenever they turned the water into wine, Mary said, 'Whatever He tells you to do, do it.'They didn't walk by and say, 'Jesus, fill the pots with water too.

00:13:54.232 --> 00:14:08.078
Get it all ready and you do it all, Lord, and just supernaturally do it with your holy angel choir.'They said, 'Whatever He tells you to do, do it.'There was a part that you had to play in it.

00:14:08.079 --> 00:14:15.979
And that's what the Lord was showing me today. We even prayed over it, and the Lord said there's a part for you to play in this.

00:14:15.980 --> 00:14:25.507
We're co-laborers. We will work together, son. But you don't sit on your blessed assurance waiting for the harvest to come in.

00:14:25.508 --> 00:14:31.142
How bad are you a contender for the harvest of souls? How bad do you want it?

00:14:31.143 --> 00:14:37.198
How bad are you going to work for Me and help Me out? He's not waiting. 'Well, send your angels, Lord.

00:14:37.199 --> 00:14:50.562
Send your Holy Ghost and fire.'We've got to put the pews down or the chairs, have a tent ready, have the fires out, tell the people to come, and then the glory comes.

00:14:50.563 --> 00:14:58.047
That's His job. He brings the glory. It's like me. The Lord said, 'I want you to go on prayer every day. I want you to do as much as you can.

00:14:58.048 --> 00:15:08.773
I know you're going to take some breaks, but I want you to make it a staple to pray and have people come pray with you, and you'll change things.'But I'm going to tell you, I brought a platform and we made computers.

00:15:08.774 --> 00:15:14.398
We got the lights. We got all this, but I can't make the gift happen.

00:15:14.399 --> 00:15:24.180
I can't turn it on. I can yield myself to Him and say, 'Father, here am I. Use me.'And if You don't show up, I'm just dabber.

00:15:24.181 --> 00:15:29.679
But whenever He puts this super on your natural, you turn into Superman.

00:15:29.680 --> 00:15:39.359
But until then, we have a treasure in earthen vessels that the excellency of the power is known of Him and not of me. I can't do anything outside of Him.

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:50.954
And most people think, like they say, these soothsayers contact you and they say, 'Brandon, come on our show.'These fortune tellers and all these people want me to come on their shows and talk to them and tell them how...

00:15:50.955 --> 00:15:56.319
I don't have nothing. Brandon doesn't have any ability to do anything.

00:15:56.320 --> 00:16:02.678
It's His ability on my flesh that allows me to see what's coming to tell you to pray.

00:16:02.679 --> 00:16:07.410
But I can't do it outside of myself. I am solely dependent on everything He tells me to do.

00:16:07.411 --> 00:16:10.313
And that's where it has to be with this end-time harvest money.

00:16:10.314 --> 00:16:15.638
I am solely dependent on You telling me what to invest in and where to put my money, Father.

00:16:15.639 --> 00:16:21.017
Because without You, I can do nothing. Show me what You want me to do.

00:16:21.018 --> 00:16:28.186
And I will not move until I hear Your voice. That's why you get quiet.

00:16:28.187 --> 00:16:34.714
There's so much clutter. There's so much static. People are always trying to hurry God. They're microwave. 'Well, Brandon, you pray too long.

00:16:34.715 --> 00:16:43.359
Boy, you think a lot about yourself praying for two hours.'No, it's me trying to cultivate a relationship.

00:16:43.360 --> 00:16:47.999
If my life doesn't display relationship, then don't watch me.

00:16:48.000 --> 00:16:57.999
But I'm trying. Hey, I love you. I'm here. I'll help you however I can with this vessel.

00:16:58.000 --> 00:17:02.270
And if You can put that treasure inside of me and use it today, then use it.

00:17:02.271 --> 00:17:11.918
If not, then I'm going to go on about my business and try to do something with my hands to provide for my family.

00:17:11.919 --> 00:17:18.399
But either way, Lord, You told me to work. A man that doesn't provide for his own is worse than an infidel.

00:17:18.400 --> 00:17:22.719
I will do whatever I've got to do to provide for my wife and my kids.

00:17:22.720 --> 00:17:29.539
And you know what? That's the way I think any godly man or any woman should be.

00:17:29.540 --> 00:17:36.959
Maybe your husband can't work, but anybody that doesn't provide for his own is worse than an infidel.

00:17:36.960 --> 00:17:41.832
Try to take care and do something. Put your boat into motion.

00:17:41.833 --> 00:17:50.959
Stop being lazy. That's why I tell people... They say, 'Brandon, what do you do?'I do whatever I can.

00:17:50.960 --> 00:17:54.618
If I have to mow grass, I'll mow grass. If I have to clean a car, I'll clean a car.

00:17:54.619 --> 00:18:02.079
You don't know how many cars I cleaned. Detail business, polishing wheels, whatever you've got to do, you do it.

00:18:02.080 --> 00:18:08.052
Especially when you're not real smart. You keep pushing and you keep doing whatever you've got to do.

00:18:08.053 --> 00:18:15.526
And some days are easier than others. But you know, God is able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:18:15.527 --> 00:18:27.119
I believe in the power of the seed. I bring all that up because of where we are in these end times, and I know the storm is coming.

00:18:27.120 --> 00:18:31.243
I know where we are by the Spirit of God. We are at that little...

00:18:31.244 --> 00:18:35.678
I feel a calm right now today. I felt like we did something—we diffused something huge.

00:18:35.679 --> 00:18:45.265
It's like cutting off the Mission Impossible fuse; you cut it off and you go, "Ah, we were right there from the ignition switch."Boom.

00:18:45.266 --> 00:18:51.549
That thing was about to go off, but the body of Christ came in there with two seconds left on the clock.

00:18:51.550 --> 00:18:56.050
You have that "ah"moment in the movie, you know? That's where we were last night.

00:18:56.051 --> 00:19:05.420
We went and we cut the red wire right in time. You're sweating bullets and you go, "It didn't go.

00:19:05.421 --> 00:19:12.530
We did it! The red wire got cut."That's what I feel like we do sometimes in the spirit realm.

00:19:12.531 --> 00:19:17.836
That's where we're like Mission Impossible. We're like Jason Bourne, you know?

00:19:17.837 --> 00:19:25.038
I like those kind of movies—Mission Impossible, James Bond, the suspense.

00:19:25.039 --> 00:19:28.798
I feel like that's what we look like in the spirit realm sometimes.

00:19:28.799 --> 00:19:44.154
I always picture myself as that: "Hey, we're coming in; we're the secret assassins working for the Lord, helping diffuse things and work for Him and pray."Most people say, "Oh, Brandon, come on."No, it's a relationship.

00:19:44.155 --> 00:20:08.460
I want to be that for my Father, that we can pray and we can go into the enemy's camp and take back what he's stolen from us.

00:20:08.461 --> 00:20:18.695
"I went to the enemy's camp and I took back what he stole from me; he's under my feet,"you know.

00:20:18.696 --> 00:20:23.513
I like those old songs, but I wanted just to encourage y'all a little bit today.

00:20:23.514 --> 00:20:30.558
You see the things in the news, you see what's going on, but we have more work to do.

00:20:30.559 --> 00:20:45.442
So, let's take communion and pray. I won't take you all night; I try to keep it shorter. It's 19 minutes; it goes quick, man. Praise the Lord.

00:20:45.443 --> 00:20:53.124
I was going to tell your mama to come in and write down if the Lord wants to show us anything. But isn't it amazing? I think it's interesting.

00:20:53.125 --> 00:21:02.798
You can see so many people walking in a gift and they try to have some kind of arrogant attitude that they're doing anything.

00:21:02.799 --> 00:21:10.095
Don't you understand that He can use anybody? Don't you understand that He can touch anybody?

00:21:10.096 --> 00:21:17.226
If He can use a donkey, He can use anybody. He's not bound by us.

00:21:17.227 --> 00:21:23.599
If you get a big head and you get a bad attitude, He'll just bypass you and use somebody else.

00:21:23.600 --> 00:21:32.158
We have this treasure in earthen vessels. If He wants to show us something, we'll pray tonight, baby, and you can write it down.

00:21:32.159 --> 00:21:37.474
I love our little book because Diana takes all these notes and she has all this stuff in here of what He's told us.

00:21:37.475 --> 00:21:46.076
And this is so precious. Yeah, somebody sent it to us—I don't know who it was, but thank you.

00:21:46.077 --> 00:21:52.979
We get little treasures like that—somebody sends us a little booklet or some kind of Bible.

00:21:52.980 --> 00:22:02.079
It's really meaningful. So, Father, I thank You, Lord, for Your body. Lord, we thank You for how good You have been to us.

00:22:02.080 --> 00:22:06.539
And we thank You, Father, that You've rebuked the devourer for our sake.

00:22:06.540 --> 00:22:10.941
We thank You, Lord, that we're healed and whole and well by Your stripes.

00:22:10.942 --> 00:22:20.252
Father, I thank You that You said You rebuke the devourer for our sake.

00:22:20.253 --> 00:22:34.454
And we thank You, Father, that we be healthy, whole, and well, and everything we do in word and in deed, we give all to the glory of God.

00:22:34.455 --> 00:22:40.879
Now, if that offends whoever it is, get over it. You offend us when you send stupid emails.

00:22:40.880 --> 00:22:50.721
So, Father, we thank You for Your body in Jesus'name. Thank You, Father, for the blood.

00:22:50.722 --> 00:22:59.380
We apply the blood in Jesus'name. And we thank You, Father, for how good You've been to us and how wonderful You are.

00:22:59.381 --> 00:23:05.520
We thank You, Father, that You forgive. We make much of the blood and the blood makes much of us.

00:23:05.521 --> 00:23:17.359
We apply the blood over us in Jesus'name. And we thank You, Father, for how much You've done for us already.

00:23:17.360 --> 00:23:25.421
What can wash away our sin? Nothing but the blood of Jesus. What can make us whole again?

00:23:25.422 --> 00:23:35.519
Nothing but the blood of Jesus. Father, we take the blood right now in Jesus'name.

00:23:35.520 --> 00:23:44.399
We come boldly into Your throne in Jesus'name. Amen and amen.

00:23:44.400 --> 00:23:53.439
Well, I plead the blood over my eyes and if there's anything You want me to see, if there's anything You want me to do, Lord, we're here.

00:23:53.440 --> 00:24:02.116
And Lord, we warn the people of what's to come. We apply the blood and we thank You, Lord, for what's to come.

00:24:02.117 --> 00:24:23.430
You've been good to us and Your mercy endures forever. For the Lord is good and His mercy endures forever.

00:24:23.431 --> 00:24:32.319
And we plead the blood, Father, and great is Your faithfulness to us.

00:24:32.320 --> 00:25:01.384
Thank You, Lord. Father, we worship You. Praise You, Lord, for You're holy, holy, Lord.

00:25:01.385 --> 00:25:19.278
There is none like You. You are holy, holy. Glory to You alone.

00:25:19.279 --> 00:25:33.119
And I sing Your praises forever, ever deeper in love with You.

00:25:33.120 --> 00:28:58.239
Here in Your courts where I'm close to Your throne, that's where I found I belong.

00:28:58.240 --> 00:29:16.079
Father, You're so good. Oh, Father, fill our cup, Lord. We lift it up, Lord.

00:29:16.080 --> 00:30:52.959
Come and quench this thirsting of our soul. Bread of heaven, feed me till I want no more.

00:30:52.960 --> 00:31:10.079
Fill my cup; fill it up and make me whole. What can wash away my sin?

00:31:10.080 --> 00:31:21.519
Nothing but the blood of Jesus. What can make me whole again?

00:31:21.520 --> 00:31:43.839
Nothing but the blood of Jesus. Oh, precious is the flow that makes me white as snow.

00:31:43.840 --> 00:32:20.798
No other fount I know. Nothing but the blood of Jesus. Softly, tenderly, Jesus is calling, calling for you and for me.

00:32:20.799 --> 00:32:34.959
I like this part when he goes, "Come home. Come home. You who are weary, come home."Softly, tenderly, Jesus is waiting, waiting for you and for me.

00:32:34.960 --> 00:34:21.279
Come home. Come home. You who are weary, come home. Softly, tenderly, Jesus is waiting; all His calling is awaiting; all ye lost sinners, come home.

00:34:21.280 --> 00:34:45.519
Do you have those words, "Softly, tenderly, Jesus is waiting, all ye lost sinners, come home"?

00:34:45.520 --> 00:34:54.323
Do you have it? Let me see if I can get some of the words better. Thanks.

00:34:54.325 --> 00:35:10.078
